snippet.title: Megaquarium: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Megaquarium is a simulation game all about designing and managing your very own public aquarium.

Layout and decorate your tanks, pick your fish, hire and manage staff and try to make a profit all at the same time!

For more information check out: http://www.megaquariumgame.com

Sign up to the dev newsletter here, top of right hand side bar: http://www.twicecircled.com/2c/blog/
http://www.twitter.com/twicecircled
